I should point out that none of this code is API and that currently embedding eclipse in a webapp is not actually supported. You are free to do this kind of thing but be aware that you may have to do some porting each release, as is the case here. I will make an effort not to rework things unnecessarily until we have a real solution. However user assistance alone cannot provide this solution as it would require extra work to get the runtime to work in this new environment.

